2\\\",\\\"olive-oil-terroir-spain-greece-italy\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/blog/olive-oil-terroir-spain-greece-italy\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"group\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"article\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1c\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/21efe059834d48fdb33d24f0285fb2de_fe61b.png\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？ — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\\\",\\\"unoptimized\\\":true}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"p-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[7,\\\" 分鐘閱讀\\\"]}]]}]]}]}]]}]]}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"💬\\\"}],\\\" 常見問題\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"如何辨別橄欖油是真是假？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"辨別真假橄欖油有五個關鍵方法：(1) 查看是否標示「特級初榨 Extra Virgin」並附 IOC 或 PDO/DOP 認證；(2) 確認標示採收年份（非僅最佳食用日期）；(3) 正宗 EVOO 應在喉嚨後部產生辛辣感（Oleocanthal 的嗆感）；(4) 避免透明玻璃瓶裝（光線會加速氧化破壞多酚）；(5) 購買價格過低的「特級初榨」需提高警覺，真正高多酚油的成本難以低價販售。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"市面上橄欖油摻假問題有多嚴重？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"根據歐盟食品安全局（EFSA）調查及加州大學戴維斯分校研究，市面上標榜「特級初榨」的橄欖油中，有高達 50-80% 達不到 IOC 官方標準。常見摻假手法包括：混入精製橄欖油（Refined Olive Oil）、混入葵花籽油或菜籽油、將普通橄欖油調色後包裝成頂級品。台灣市場同樣面臨此問題，特別是低價進口品牌。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"PDO/DOP 認證能保證橄欖油品質嗎？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"PDO（Protected Designation of Origin，歐盟原產地保護）和 DOP（Denominazione di Origine Protetta，義大利同等認證）確保橄欖油的原料來源和加工地點，但不直接保證多酚含量。具備認證代表來源可追溯，但若要確認多酚品質，還需查看 CoA（分析證明書）中的總酚含量（TPC）數值，理想值為 ≥250mg/kg。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油冷藏後會凝固，凝固表示是真品嗎？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油在低溫（4-10°C）下確實會開始凝固或出現蠟質沉澱，這是橄欖油中飽和脂肪酸和蠟質的自然現象。但這並非可靠的真偽鑑別方法，因為部分調和油也可能在低溫下凝固。最可靠的鑑別方式仍是認證標籤、採收年份標示、來源追溯和感官測試（嗆感與苦味）。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leadi